sourcesContent:
const quotes = [
    "Be happy for this moment. This moment is your life. - Omar Khayyam",
    "A hair divides what is false and true. - Omar Khayyam",
    "You are not a drop in the ocean. You are the entire ocean, in a drop. - Rumi",
    "You have to keep breaking your heart until it opens. - Rumi",
    "Raise your words, not your voice. For it is rain that grows flowers, not thunder. - Rumi",
    "One does not attain everything he wishes for. Winds blow counter to what the ships desire. - Al-Mutanabbi",
    "I wish I could show you...the astonishing light of your own being. - Hafez",
    "The heart is a thousand-stringed instrument that can only be tuned with love. - Hafez"
]

export default quotes;
